OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBright
OL,6,Fspells and showers, these becoming
OL,7,Fless frequent during the evening.
OL,8,FClear spells increase for a time from
OL,9,Flate evening but cloud and rain spread
OL,10,Fnortheast overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CFriday:FEarly cloud and rain soon
OL,13,Fclear northeast to leave the morning
OL,14,Fdry with sunny spells. The odd shower
OL,15,Fwill develop during the afternoon.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
